title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2015-06-25 Episode 004 - MP4 MP3
description:
*** CAUTION: 100% UNCENSORED CONTENT!!! ***

-NOT FOR VIEWING BY CHILDREN OR THE FAINT OF HEART-

The always outspoken and "controversial" Gavin McInnes joins the Anthony Cumia Network - with new shows twice a week. In addition to co-founding VICE, the author, actor, musician, podcast host, and political pundit is at the forefront of the modern "anti-PC" movement and a perfect match for the cutting edge and newly emerging ACN.


Guests: HK Edgerton, Ian Shive, Mercedes Carrera, Razib Khan

Episode 004: Gavin starts the show asking Ian Shive who he'd rather fight a shark or squid. Gavin gets into the causes of the Civil War and his #TakeUsDown movement. HK Edgerton calls in to defend the Confederate flag and Dylann Roof. Razib Khan has some trouble with Skype while he tries to explain CRISPRs. Gavin is mesmerized by Mercedes Carrera as they discuss the porn business. Gavin ends the show talking about Brendan Eich and taking calls.
